{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.1","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:1","prev_osis_id":"Num.017.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Fonctions et revenus des sacrificateurs et des L\u00e9vites<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-7: cf. (No 3. 1 Ch 23:13, 24-32. No 8:14-19.) Ps 65:5.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 Aaron: Toi et tes fils, et la maison de ton p\u00e8re avec toi, vous porterez la peine des iniquit\u00e9s commises dans le sanctuaire; toi et tes fils avec toi, vous porterez la peine des iniquit\u00e9s commises dans l\u2019exercice de votre sacerdoce.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.2","name":"Nombres 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.17.13","name":"Nombres 17:13","id":"fra-LSG:Num.17.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.2","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:2","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Fais aussi approcher de toi tes fr\u00e8res, la tribu de L\u00e9vi, la tribu de ton p\u00e8re, afin qu\u2019ils te soient attach\u00e9s et qu\u2019ils te servent, lorsque toi, et tes fils avec toi, vous serez devant la tente du t\u00e9moignage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.3","name":"Nombres 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.1","name":"Nombres 18:1","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.3","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:3","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Ils observeront ce que tu leur ordonneras et ce qui concerne toute la tente; mais ils ne s\u2019approcheront ni des ustensiles du sanctuaire, ni de l\u2019autel, de peur que vous ne mouriez, eux et vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.4","name":"Nombres 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.2","name":"Nombres 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.4","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:4","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Ils te seront attach\u00e9s, et ils observeront ce qui concerne la tente d\u2019assignation pour tout le service de la tente. Aucun \u00e9tranger n\u2019approchera de vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.5","name":"Nombres 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.3","name":"Nombres 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.5","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:5","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Vous observerez ce qui concerne le sanctuaire et l\u2019autel, afin qu\u2019il n\u2019y ait plus de col\u00e8re contre les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.6","name":"Nombres 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.4","name":"Nombres 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.6","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:6","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Voici, j\u2019ai pris vos fr\u00e8res les L\u00e9vites du milieu des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: donn\u00e9s \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ils vous sont remis en don pour faire le service de la tente d\u2019assignation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.7","name":"Nombres 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.5","name":"Nombres 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.7","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:7","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Toi, et tes fils avec toi, vous observerez les fonctions de votre sacerdoce pour tout ce qui concerne l\u2019autel et pour ce qui est en dedans du voile: c\u2019est le service que vous ferez. Je vous accorde en pur don l\u2019exercice du sacerdoce. L\u2019\u00e9tranger qui approchera sera mis \u00e0 mort.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.8","name":"Nombres 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.6","name":"Nombres 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.8","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:8","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.009,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 8-19: cf. (L\u00e9 7:7-14, 29-36. \u00c9z 44:29, 30.) 1 Co 9:13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 Aaron: Voici, de toutes les choses que consacrent les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, je te donne celles qui me sont offertes par \u00e9l\u00e9vation; je te les donne, \u00e0 toi et \u00e0 tes fils, comme droit d\u2019onction, par une loi perp\u00e9tuelle.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.9","name":"Nombres 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.7","name":"Nombres 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.9","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:9","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Voici ce qui t\u2019appartiendra parmi les choses tr\u00e8s saintes qui ne sont pas consum\u00e9es par le feu: toutes leurs offrandes, tous leurs dons, tous leurs sacrifices d\u2019expiation, et tous les sacrifices de culpabilit\u00e9 qu\u2019ils m\u2019offriront; ces choses tr\u00e8s saintes seront pour toi et pour tes fils.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.10","name":"Nombres 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.8","name":"Nombres 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.10","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:10","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Vous les mangerez dans un lieu tr\u00e8s saint; tout m\u00e2le en mangera; vous les regarderez comme saintes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.11","name":"Nombres 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.9","name":"Nombres 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.11","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:11","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Voici encore ce qui t\u2019appartiendra: tous les dons que les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl pr\u00e9senteront par \u00e9l\u00e9vation et en les agitant de c\u00f4t\u00e9 et d\u2019autre, je te les donne \u00e0 toi, \u00e0 tes fils et \u00e0 tes filles avec toi, par une loi perp\u00e9tuelle. Quiconque sera pur dans ta maison en mangera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.12","name":"Nombres 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.10","name":"Nombres 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.12","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:12","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Je te donne les pr\u00e9mices qu\u2019ils offriront \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel: tout ce qu\u2019il y aura de meilleur en huile, tout ce qu\u2019il y aura de meilleur en mo\u00fbt et en bl\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.13","name":"Nombres 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.11","name":"Nombres 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.13","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:13","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Les premiers produits de leur terre, qu\u2019ils apporteront \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, seront pour toi. Quiconque sera pur dans ta maison en mangera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.14","name":"Nombres 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.12","name":"Nombres 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.14","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:14","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Tout ce qui sera d\u00e9vou\u00e9 par interdit en Isra\u00ebl sera pour toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.15","name":"Nombres 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.13","name":"Nombres 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.15","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:15","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Tout premier-n\u00e9 de toute chair, qu\u2019ils offriront \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, tant des hommes que des animaux, sera pour toi. Seulement, tu feras racheter le premier-n\u00e9 de l\u2019homme, et tu feras racheter le premier-n\u00e9 d\u2019un animal impur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.16","name":"Nombres 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.14","name":"Nombres 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.16","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:16","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Tu les feras racheter d\u00e8s l\u2019\u00e2ge d\u2019un mois, d\u2019apr\u00e8s ton estimation, au prix de cinq sicles d\u2019argent, selon le sicle du sanctuaire, qui est de vingt gu\u00e9ras.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.17","name":"Nombres 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.15","name":"Nombres 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.17","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:17","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Mais tu ne feras point racheter le premier-n\u00e9 du b\u0153uf, ni le premier-n\u00e9 de la brebis, ni le premier-n\u00e9 de la ch\u00e8vre: ce sont des choses saintes. Tu r\u00e9pandras leur sang sur l\u2019autel, et tu br\u00fbleras leur graisse: ce sera un sacrifice consum\u00e9 par le feu, d\u2019une agr\u00e9able odeur \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.18","name":"Nombres 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.16","name":"Nombres 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.18","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:18","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Leur chair sera pour toi, comme la poitrine qu\u2019on agite de c\u00f4t\u00e9 et d\u2019autre et comme l\u2019\u00e9paule droite.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.19","name":"Nombres 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.17","name":"Nombres 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.19","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:19","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Je te donne, \u00e0 toi, \u00e0 tes fils et \u00e0 tes filles avec toi, par une loi perp\u00e9tuelle, toutes les offrandes saintes que les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl pr\u00e9senteront \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel par \u00e9l\u00e9vation. C\u2019est une alliance inviolable et \u00e0 perp\u00e9tuit\u00e9 devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, pour toi et pour ta post\u00e9rit\u00e9 avec toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.20","name":"Nombres 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.18","name":"Nombres 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.20","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:20","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.021,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 20-24: cf. (\u00c9z 44:28. L\u00e9 27:30-33.) N\u00e9 10:37. Mal 3:8-10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 Aaron: Tu ne poss\u00e9deras rien dans leur pays, et il n\u2019y aura point de part pour toi au milieu d\u2019eux; c\u2019est moi qui suis ta part et ta possession, au milieu des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.21","name":"Nombres 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.19","name":"Nombres 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.21","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:21","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Je donne comme possession aux fils de L\u00e9vi toute d\u00eeme en Isra\u00ebl, pour le service qu\u2019ils font, le service de la tente d\u2019assignation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.22","name":"Nombres 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.20","name":"Nombres 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.22","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:22","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl n\u2019approcheront plus de la tente d\u2019assignation, de peur qu\u2019ils ne se chargent d\u2019un p\u00e9ch\u00e9 et qu\u2019ils ne meurent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.23","name":"Nombres 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.21","name":"Nombres 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.23","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:23","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Les L\u00e9vites feront le service de la tente d\u2019assignation, et ils resteront charg\u00e9s de leurs iniquit\u00e9s. Ils n\u2019auront point de possession au milieu des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: ce sera une loi perp\u00e9tuelle parmi vos descendants.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.24","name":"Nombres 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.22","name":"Nombres 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.24","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:24","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Je donne comme possession aux L\u00e9vites les d\u00eemes que les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl pr\u00e9senteront \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel par \u00e9l\u00e9vation; c\u2019est pourquoi je dis \u00e0 leur \u00e9gard: Ils n\u2019auront point de possession au milieu des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.25","name":"Nombres 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.23","name":"Nombres 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.25","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:25","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.026,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 25-32: cf. N\u00e9 10:38. 1 Ti 5:17, 18.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel parla \u00e0 Mo\u00efse, et dit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.26","name":"Nombres 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.24","name":"Nombres 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.26","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:26","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Tu parleras aux L\u00e9vites, et tu leur diras: Lorsque vous recevrez des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl la d\u00eeme que je vous donne de leur part comme votre possession, vous en pr\u00e9l\u00e8verez une offrande pour l\u2019\u00c9ternel, une d\u00eeme de la d\u00eeme;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.27","name":"Nombres 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.25","name":"Nombres 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.27","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:27","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>et votre offrande vous sera compt\u00e9e comme le bl\u00e9 qu\u2019on pr\u00e9l\u00e8ve de l\u2019aire et comme le mo\u00fbt qu\u2019on pr\u00e9l\u00e8ve de la cuve.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.28","name":"Nombres 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.26","name":"Nombres 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.28","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:28","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>C\u2019est ainsi que vous pr\u00e9l\u00e8verez une offrande pour l\u2019\u00c9ternel sur toutes les d\u00eemes que vous recevrez des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et vous donnerez au sacrificateur Aaron l\u2019offrande que vous en aurez pr\u00e9lev\u00e9e pour l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.29","name":"Nombres 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.27","name":"Nombres 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.29","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:29","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Sur tous les dons qui vous seront faits, vous pr\u00e9l\u00e8verez toutes les offrandes pour l\u2019\u00c9ternel; sur tout ce qu\u2019il y aura de meilleur, vous pr\u00e9l\u00e8verez la portion consacr\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.30","name":"Nombres 18:30","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.28","name":"Nombres 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.30","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:30","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Tu leur diras: Quand vous en aurez pr\u00e9lev\u00e9 le meilleur, la d\u00eeme sera compt\u00e9e aux L\u00e9vites comme le revenu de l\u2019aire et comme le revenu de la cuve.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.31","name":"Nombres 18:31","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.29","name":"Nombres 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.31","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:31","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.018.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Vous la mangerez en un lieu quelconque, vous et votre maison; car c\u2019est votre salaire pour le service que vous faites dans la tente d\u2019assignation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.32","name":"Nombres 18:32","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.30","name":"Nombres 18:30","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Num.18.32","label":"","reference":"Nombres 18:32","prev_osis_id":"Num.018.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Num.019.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Num.18.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Vous ne serez charg\u00e9s pour cela d\u2019aucun p\u00e9ch\u00e9, quand vous en aurez pr\u00e9lev\u00e9 le meilleur, vous ne profanerez point les offrandes saintes des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et vous ne mourrez point.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Num.18","name":"Nombres 18","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.19.1","name":"Nombres 19:1","id":"fra-LSG:Num.19.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Num.18.31","name":"Nombres 18:31","id":"fra-LSG:Num.18.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81f8198ac82.77229663');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81f8198ac82.77229663\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81f8198ac82.77229663","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81f8198ac82.77229663'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81f8198ac82.77229663\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}